item.description:
Let's go check out the comedy show at the Winner's Circle


The Winner's Circle has a FREE Comedy show every Tuesday in their Skybox function room they have different comedians every week. Let's go check them out and have some almost mid week laughs.

The comedy show starts approx 8:00pm, let's meetup early grab some dinner, get our seats, then sit back and watch the show.

They have a great pub menu check it out here: http://www.winnerscir...

Cost: For the show FREE
Parking: Plenty of parking in there parking lot.

Looking forward to seeing you!
Donna
item.how_to_find_us: I will be outside near the entrance.
